survminer::ggsurvplot(
    fit = survival::survfit(survival::Surv(OS.time, OS) ~ gender, data = tcga_meta), 
    xlab = "Days",
    ylab = "Overall survival probability",
    legend.title = "Rx Group",
    censor = TRUE,
    pval = TRUE)
